com.kaichunlin.transition

Class BaseTransitionBuilder<T extends BaseTransitionBuilder,U extends ITransition>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kaichunlin.transition.BaseTransitionBuilder<T,U>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MenuItemTransitionBuilder, ViewTransitionBuilder

    public abstract class BaseTransitionBuilder<T extends BaseTransitionBuilder,U extends ITransition>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Provides foundation to build classes that allows easy creation of ITransition

    Created by Kai-Chun Lin on 2015/4/23.
